title: Ep. 63 - Time To Sell Momentum Stocks
itunes:title: Time To Sell Momentum Stocks
description: Jeff Clark, editor of S&A's Short Report options service, tells us why the sell-off in momentum names could lead to a short-term correction. Keith Fitzgerald, chief investment strategist for Money Map Press, talks about the enormous growth opportunities that still exist in China.
